<h2>🚨 URGENT TIMETABLE UPDATE</h2>

<p>Hello,</p>

<p>This is an <strong style="color: #dc2626;">URGENT</strong> notification regarding your timetable for <strong>{{batchName}}</strong>.</p>

<div class="urgent-box">
    <strong style="color: #dc2626; font-size: 16px;">⚠️ Important Update</strong>
    <p style="margin: 15px 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">
        {{updateMessage}}
    </p>
    <ul style="margin: 10px 0;">
        <li><strong>Effective From:</strong> {{formatDate effectiveDate}}</li>
        <li><strong>Updated By:</strong> {{updatedBy}}</li>
        <li><strong>Priority:</strong> <span style="color: #dc2626; text-transform: uppercase;">{{priority}}</span></li>
    </ul>
</div>

<p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="{{scheduleUrl}}" class="button" style="background: #dc2626;">View Updated Schedule Now</a>
</p>

<p><strong style="color: #dc2626;">IMMEDIATE ACTIONS REQUIRED:</strong></p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Review the updated schedule immediately</strong></li>
    <li>Adjust your plans accordingly</li>
    <li>Inform fellow students and coordinate with them</li>
    <li>Contact faculty if you have scheduling conflicts</li>
    <li>Check for any additional communications</li>
</ul>

<div class="info-box">
    <strong>📞 Need Help?</strong>
    <p style="margin: 5px 0;">If you have any questions or concerns about this update, please contact:</p>
    <ul style="margin: 5px 0;">
        <li>Class Coordinator</li>
        <li>HOD Office</li>
        <li>Email: {{supportEmail}}</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<p style="font-weight: 600; color: #dc2626;">
    Please acknowledge this update by checking your schedule within the next 24 hours.
</p>

<p>Best regards,<br><strong>Academic Administration</strong></p>
